column5: Anyone head out from there today? I'm planning to go up Monday, hopefully all this rain doesn't trash the walk-on access too much... anyone who heads out Sunday please let me know how it was! Thanks...
If you listen to the MEDIA,you should STAY off the ice,IT,S NOT SAFE. Bull Friggn   ,sssss dont know squat. If yer walking ,alls good. We did the drive today, and theres no worries.
nights are below zero - with no snow on the ice, everything tightens up.  tons of ice, was like walking on concrete today on simcoe, bring creepers.
Thanks guys, looks like Monday will be a go...
